headline: Assessing Corteva (CTVA) Valuation After New Biofuel Ventures And Fresh Analyst Upgrade
summary: Corteva (CTVA) shares are in focus after the company announced Etlas, a 50:50 joint venture with bp to produce crop based feedstocks for sustainable aviation fuel and renewable diesel at scale. See our latest analysis for Corteva. Corteva’s recent partnerships, including Etlas with bp and the Hexagon Bio tie up, have arrived against a backdrop of gradually improving momentum.
